    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>dill</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped dill</strong> and <strong>mayo</strong> in a small bowl with the <strong>juice</strong> of <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> and a pinch of salt and pepper – this is your <strong>herby lemon mayo</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lemon </strong>into wedges</p>",
