    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>blanched peas</strong> to a pot, cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook for 1 min or until they're warmed through, then drain and return to the pot with the <strong>mint sauce</strong>, a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Mash the peas until they come together nicely – these are your <strong>minted peas</strong></p>",
