      "instruction": "<p>Cut a slit into the top of your<strong> hot dog bun[s]</strong></p><p>Once the fish fingers are nearly done, remove the tray[s] from the oven and add the <strong>cut</strong> <strong>hot dog bun[s]</strong> to the baking tray[s]</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for 2-3 min or until warmed through</p>",
