    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build, spread a spoonful of the <strong>minted peas </strong>in the <strong>warmed hot dog bun </strong>and top with the <strong>basa fish fingers</strong> and a drizzle of the <strong>herby lemon mayo</strong> – these are your <strong>basa fish finger dogs</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> basa fish finger dogs </strong>with the <strong>chips</strong>, <strong>remaining minted peas</strong>, and <strong>tomato ketchup </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
